## Common Mistakes

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| `import { View } from 'react-native'` | `import { View } from '@/components'` |
| `containerStyle: 'variantDefault'` | `containerStyle: styles.variantDefault` |
| `enum Variant { A = 'a' }` | `type Variant = 'a' \| 'b'` |
| `{loading ? <Spinner /> : content}` | `{loading && <Spinner />}{content}` |
| `backgroundColor: '#000'` | `backgroundColor: theme.colors.primary` |
| No accessibility props | Add role, state, labels |

